{"title":"LAC - Formal Languages and Automata Theory 形式语言与自动机理论","uid":"49266c0927eaad653ea21227e55d59fb","slug":"笔记/笔记-LAC-形式语言与自动机","date":"2024-05-25T10:53:20.000Z","updated":"2024-05-27T17:59:11.108Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/笔记/笔记-LAC-形式语言与自动机.json","keywords":null,"cover":"\\img\\post\\笔记\\笔记-LAC-形式语言与自动机\\cover.png","content":"<h1 id=\"背景\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#背景\"></a> 背景</h1>\n<p>课程原名为Languages and Computation(语言与计算)，但是这很明显是一个比较笼统的名字。本课程的主要内容还是将有关形式语言与自动机理论的知识。</p>\n<p>关于自动机，早在学习算法竞赛的时候有学过AC自动机(Aho-Corasick automaton, 是字典树 + KMP算法 + 自动机的结合)的知识，但是并没有建立有关自动机的系统性概念。</p>\n<p>此外，在学习做游戏AI的时候，有接触过关于状态设计模式的概念，游戏AI是一个巨大的状态自动机，因此我也利用这个方法在我CPP课程的游戏里设计了敌人的AI，具体可以参考这个笔记: <a href=\"\">简单游戏引擎开发笔记</a>。</p>\n<h1 id=\"介绍\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#介绍\"></a> 介绍</h1>\n<p>本笔记主要分为下面几个部分(并不是按照课程顺序排序，而是相似课程归纳)：</p>\n","feature":false,"text":"有关形式语言与自动机理论的课程笔记。...","permalink":"/post/笔记/笔记-LAC-形式语言与自动机","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":325,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","count":3,"path":"api/categories/笔记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Notes","slug":"Notes","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Notes.json"},{"name":"Automata Theory","slug":"Automata-Theory","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Automata-Theory.json"},{"name":"Formal Languages","slug":"Formal-Languages","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Formal-Languages.json"},{"name":"Theory","slug":"Theory","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Theory.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 背景</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 介绍</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"zExNocs","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个喜欢摸鱼的人。<p>去码头整点薯条。</p>","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","cus